FBIS4-15470 "drsov068_a_94020" FBIS-SOV-94-068 Daily Report 7 Apr 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Talks With Belarus Encounter `Great Difficulties' Talks With Belarus Encounter `Great Difficulties' LD0704224794 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network in Russian 1700 GMT 7 Apr 94 LD0704224794 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network Russian BFN [From the "Novosti" newscast] [Text] The talks between Russia and Belarus on uniting the monetary systems of the two countries are proceeding with great difficulties. The regular round of talks was held in Moscow 4-7 April and failed to fully resolve the main disagreements.
